Packager: Victor Forsyuk <force@altlinux.org>

Summary: GIMP plugin for image sharpening using wavelets
License: GPLv2+
Group: Graphics

Url: http://registry.gimp.org/node/9836
Source: http://registry.gimp.org/files/wavelet-sharpen-%version.tar.gz
